1月8日赴武漢出差，16日返京，當日出現發熱和呼吸道症狀，20日在本市醫療機構就診，21日確診為新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎病例；<br />\n二、魯某某，男，1月10日赴武漢出差，11日返京，14日出現發熱症狀，20日在本市醫療機構就診，21日確診為新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎病例；<br />\n三、閻某，男，1月3日至10日曾到大連、吉林白山、長春等地旅行，14日參加會議時與上述病例魯某某座位相鄰，18日出現發熱症狀，20日在本市醫療機構就診，25日確診為新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎病例。目前三名醫生均在定點醫院接受隔離治療，病情平穩，密切接觸者都已納入隔離醫學觀察，未報告異常情況。<br />\n<br />\n支持醫護人員任何行動，香港政府罔顧醫護人員安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655debdfe5eac7aaf3a762073d30d46619e8e066","tid":1842790,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"新鮮滾熱護士崩潰片<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/vftjf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fvftjf&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=197e4fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/vftjf</a>"},{"pid":"185f1a5262b728426a98bf789acff9b18e2ebc14","tid":1842790,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"等緊醫護吹雞, 你罷我罷"},{"pid":"d624a44434475820c0205a050eab700828efc317","tid":1842790,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27bdae591624d1f4ffdacdc641fce5a0390c5d73","tid":1842790,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccf6e487e7ca75969bd710e8003a859a3c099362","tid":1842790,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f732f8e4bb3106ff47ddc59116cb3f0e273ae202","tid":1842790,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:23:29.000Z","msg":"屌，又唔見佢支持罷工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"成個醫護界都無guts<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等出事啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"黃醫生點會無guts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"有吉屎就應該帶頭即時罷工<br />\n唔好等<br />\n比人炒又如何？無左條命 乜都唔駛講"}],"pinned":{"pid":"655debdfe5eac7aaf3a762073d30d46619e8e066","tid":1842790,"uid":126621,"like":0